1
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,200
Yang Yunfan

2
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:44,359
You've passed the Mystic Water Hall trial.

3
00:01:44,359 --> 00:01:47,120
Take an oath before the Medicine Venerable,

4
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,599
and receive the seal,

5
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:50,760
to become an official Apothecary.

6
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:59,200
I shall follow the Medicine Venerable's words.

7
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,359
A carefree wanderer walks the healing path,

8
00:02:01,359 --> 00:02:03,000
doing good deeds without seeking fame.

9
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:08,639
A carefree wanderer walks the healing path,

10
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:11,159
doing good deeds without seeking fame.

11
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:14,840
Yang Yunfan.

12
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,439
Yang Yunfan!

13
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,840
Do you vow to uphold this path?

14
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:28,360
This disciple, Yang Yunfan,

15
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,400
so vows.

16
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:29,960
Wrong.

17
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:33,080
It's Apothecary Yang Yunfan.

18
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:41,039
Apothecary Yang Yunfan

19
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:43,080
vows to uphold a healer's benevolence,

20
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,400
to save lives and aid the world,

21
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,639
never use my arts to harm,

22
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,120
never betray the healing path,

23
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,919
nor the Medicine Venerable.

24
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:04,520
The Medicine Venerable bestows the seal.

25
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,000
Walk the path of healing.

26
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:36,800
This is the Living Seal.

27
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,759
I've never seen one before.

28
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:40,039
What's that in his hand?

29
00:03:41,159 --> 00:03:41,919
The Living Seal.

30
00:03:41,919 --> 00:03:42,599
It's the Living Seal.

31
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,120
He's truly no ordinary person.

32
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,159
The ceremony is complete.

33
00:03:53,159 --> 00:03:54,479
Everyone is dismissed.

34
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:04,719
Is the Living Seal a big deal?

35
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:09,919
Only those recognized by the Medicine Venerable

36
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:11,159
can manifest the Living Seal.

37
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,599
I told you long ago.

38
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:17,279
I'm definitely a peerless prodigy.

39
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,800
I like your confidence.

40
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:23,439
But the Mystic Medicine Association is full of confident people.

41
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,639
The trial is finally over.

42
00:04:32,639 --> 00:04:34,040
Now I can relax a bit.

43
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,800
Boss Ye, don't forget to treat me to a feast.

44
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,519
As a little reward, you know?

45
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:42,160
The Medicine King Festival's Medicine Holder trial is soon.

46
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,920
Only by becoming a Medicine Holder

47
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,360
will you have a voice in the Mystic Medicine Association.

48
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,720
Only then can you actually help me.

49
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,920
You're kidding.

50
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,040
Another trial?

51
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:51,319
Why is it never-ending?

52
00:04:51,759 --> 00:04:52,639
Since you're already here,

53
00:04:52,639 --> 00:04:53,720
just see it through to the end.

54
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,439
What are you two doing?

55
00:04:59,319 --> 00:05:00,759
Boss Ye.

56
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:02,560
You don't even consult me anymore.

57
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,920
One wrong move ruins the whole game.

58
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,519
If we hadn't failed the earlier trial,

59
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,160
how could the great Lu family

60
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,160
be bested by some wild kid?

61
00:05:13,439 --> 00:05:15,680
It's all your fault, you fickle woman!

62
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:17,279
If you hadn't brought such a shady guy

63
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:18,519
into Heaven Number One,

64
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:19,959
we wouldn't be in this mess.

65
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:21,160
Now look what's happened.

66
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:22,759
Even Brother-in-law is displeased with you.

67
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:27,120
He probably won't help us anymore.

68
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:32,519
In-law, what brings you here in person?

69
00:05:32,519 --> 00:05:33,879
Have a seat.

70
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:35,759
We could have just gone over to you.

71
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:38,319
He's awake.

72
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:41,120
Or should I take him to the Mystic Water Hall?

73
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:43,720
Why is Miss Lu getting personally involved?

74
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,639
Does the new advisor know her?

75
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:48,399
Maybe. I just saw them whispering.

76
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:49,920
Hurry up.

77
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,120
Pour some water.

78
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,600
In-law.

79
00:06:14,079 --> 00:06:15,120
Go.

80
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:30,279
Number Zero's identity is still unclear.

81
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,160
And now a Yang family orphan shows up?

82
00:06:32,959 --> 00:06:33,759
My dear in-law.

83
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:36,240
This all happened so suddenly.

84
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:36,959
We didn't see it coming either.

85
00:06:38,319 --> 00:06:39,839
It's all that damned Ye Qingxue's fault.

86
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:41,360
If it weren't for her,

87
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,879
we'd have taken that boy down already.

88
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:45,879
So have you confirmed his real identity?

89
00:06:46,439 --> 00:06:47,600
We're looking into it.

90
00:06:53,319 --> 00:06:56,000
Ye Qingxue has always been restless.

91
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,560
Trying to control the Mystic Medicine Association.

92
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,959
That country bumpkin's identity

93
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:02,639
was almost certainly forged by her.

94
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:03,839
Brother-in-law is right.

95
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:06,800
But this man can use the Sea-Calming Mantra.

96
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,720
Whether or not he's Yang Yunfan,

97
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,240
we must be on our guard.

98
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:16,120
Alright, I'll leave it to you.

99
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,120
Don't worry.

100
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:20,560
You know how many people are eyeing

101
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:22,600
the Mystic Water Hall's position.

102
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:23,759
Yes.

103
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:25,519
Since I helped you up there,

104
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,600
I can also pull you down.

105
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:29,560
Rest assured, In-law.

106
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,040
Rest assured.

107
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,959
This time, I definitely won't spare that brat.

108
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:34,920
Slow down.

109
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,600
After searching for so many days,

110
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,000
you missed Number Zero right under our noses.

111
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,319
Why do I even keep you?

112
00:07:54,319 --> 00:07:55,839
This subordinate is incompetent.

113
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:56,439
I was one step behind you, Venerable.

114
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:00,920
However,

115
00:08:01,399 --> 00:08:02,639
the Sea-Calming Mantra

116
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:05,079
has been taken back from Ye Qingxue.

117
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:06,120
Good.

118
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,399
Ye Qingxue.

119
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,560
That little girl really has

120
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,199
been doing a lot behind our backs.

121
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,120
I'll spare your life this time.

122
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:25,600
The Medicine King Festival is about to begin.

123
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,839
Ghost Blade, you and Shadow

124
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:29,120
take this opportunity

125
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:31,519
to get rid of that Wuming,

126
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:33,559
lest he stirs up more trouble.

127
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:36,639
Understood.

128
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,519
All right.

129
00:08:48,519 --> 00:08:49,679
Give me a moment.

130
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:50,559
Young Master Yang.

131
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:51,759
Your bedroom isn't in this direction.

132
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:54,000
I know. Just out for a stroll.

133
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:54,759
A stroll.

134
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,080
This fountain...

135
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:57,720
Sure is a big fountain.

136
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,080
Young Master, I'll be off then.

137
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,720
Okay.

138
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,120
All right, I'll be right there.

139
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,600
Tell me the exact location.

140
00:09:03,559 --> 00:09:04,200
Okay.

141
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:38,720
This is...

142
00:09:39,639 --> 00:09:40,240
Let's see...

143
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:03,120
Why is it all investigation files and medical books?

144
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:21,000
"Notes on Sui Qi"

145
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:32,960
Sui Qi is corrupted energy.

146
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:36,039
It corrodes, devours, and destroys.

147
00:10:36,759 --> 00:10:37,799
It has shadow but no form.

148
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:40,200
Ordinary people can hardly perceive it.

149
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:47,200
Master, I'll avenge you.

150
00:10:49,799 --> 00:10:51,120
Could my amnesia

151
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,840
be linked to Sui Qi?

152
00:11:11,919 --> 00:11:13,240
The Mystic Medicine Association

153
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:17,039
has a traitor.

154
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,080
It's him.

155
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:30,120
The grandfather Qingxue spoke of,

156
00:11:31,519 --> 00:11:32,559
Fuguang, the Medicine Sovereign

157
00:11:38,159 --> 00:11:40,559
Who exactly is the traitor he mentioned?

158
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:54,879
I never expected

159
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,200
that he'd actually return.

160
00:11:58,399 --> 00:12:00,919
I was also surprised when I saw him.

161
00:12:02,639 --> 00:12:04,320
It's time we set our plan in motion.

162
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:07,720
Is everything ready for the Medicine King Festival?

163
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:09,080
This is our

164
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:11,559
last chance.

165
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,279
Don't worry.

166
00:12:13,279 --> 00:12:14,799
This time, we'll catch them all in one swoop.

167
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:19,840
You're in luck today.

168
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,679
You're the only one getting this treatment.

169
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:28,039
I knew Song Ci was up to something.

170
00:12:31,519 --> 00:12:33,240
Could Ye Zhentian be the traitor?

171
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:09,720
Don't make a sound.

172
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,399
You again?

173
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:16,879
Got hurt again?

174
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:19,720
Your pulse is steady.

175
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,720
You seem to be perfectly fine.

176
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:26,440
I just came to warn you.

177
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,919
Be careful at the Medicine King Festival.

178
00:13:28,919 --> 00:13:29,879
Someone will come for your life.

179
00:13:33,759 --> 00:13:34,440
Worried about me?

180
00:13:38,159 --> 00:13:40,120
People who want me dead?

181
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:41,240
There are far too many of those.

182
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:44,240
You're the only one who poses a threat.

183
00:13:50,279 --> 00:13:51,399
I'm not joking with you.

184
00:13:53,799 --> 00:13:54,960
The Master issued a kill order on you.

185
00:13:56,399 --> 00:13:57,639
Knowing him as I do,

186
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,679
he definitely has other backup plans.

187
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,879
Who is the Master?

188
00:14:06,039 --> 00:14:06,840
The leader of Boundless.

189
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:11,200
Actually, I don't know his true identity.

190
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:13,759
I only know he's tied to the Mystic Medicine Association.

191
00:14:14,919 --> 00:14:15,799
How do you know that?

192
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:18,279
Because all our missions involve the Mystic Medicine Association.

193
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,679
Is everything ready for the Medicine King Festival?

194
00:14:22,159 --> 00:14:24,399
This is our

195
00:14:24,399 --> 00:14:25,879
last chance.

196
00:14:26,519 --> 00:14:27,480
Don't worry.

197
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:29,080
This time, we'll catch them all in one swoop.

198
00:14:33,559 --> 00:14:37,039
This Association is more cutthroat than a palace drama.

199
00:14:39,519 --> 00:14:40,960
Anyway, I've said what I had to say.

200
00:14:41,639 --> 00:14:42,399
Just be careful.

201
00:14:45,080 --> 00:14:46,279
Hold on.

202
00:14:46,279 --> 00:14:47,320
What?

203
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:49,159
Decided to switch sides and join me?

204
00:14:50,919 --> 00:14:51,519
In your dreams.

205
00:14:52,159 --> 00:14:54,519
Then please pay for the Gu poison treatment.

206
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:56,639
Or,

207
00:14:56,639 --> 00:14:57,799
you could do something for me.

208
00:15:01,519 --> 00:15:02,320
Just this once.

209
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:09,120
Put it on my tab for now.

210
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:13,919
I locked the back door...

211
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,080
How did she still get out?

212
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:31,759
No, I need to go back and look.
